items.title: Premier Partner
items.text: Genesis Ventures is a European early-stage venture capital firm based in Athens, Greece, backing bold founders from day zero. With a focus on pre-seed and seed investments, Genesis supports startups across sectors with capital, operational support, and a strong founder-first ethos. The firm has built a growing portfolio of over 45 companies and was recently named one of Europes most active VCs by Sifted. As part of its mission to empower the next generation of entrepreneurs, Genesis Ventures is a strategic supporter of the Workearly Startup Summer School, championing the development of future startup talent. Through this partnership, Genesis actively contributes to building a stronger entrepreneurial ecosystem  giving aspiring founders access to top-tier training, real-world exposure, and the confidence to launch with impact.
